​Information Collection and Use​
For a better experience, while using our Service, we may require you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information. The information that we request is will be retained by us and used as described in this privacy policy.
Data within the shared definition, classified under the CCPA as ‘Personal Information’, includes Device Identification, purchase history (from only within our applications) and advertising identifiers. This information is shared to perform advertising attribution, for the indication of performance of campaigns, and the ability to serve ads based on the users preferences and settings. PlaySide does not knowingly collect or share data that fits the definitions of ‘Sensitive Information’, in the CCPA/CPRA
